This paper deals with the optimization of resource allocation and pricing in a cloud federation, which involves distributed systems, game theory, networking, control engineering, and computer engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
